61870,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"行動呀！！！！<br />\n唔好講完就算<br />\n要實際做出嚟"},{"pid":"1f13b69d70b7c014c23694369326e75c3daa4dc2","tid":1361870,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"職業少到連保安看更都可以阻止警犬攞閉路電視錄影帶<br />\n你嘅行動一定有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb504bee33af8bb3ddf3bdf8cb755ec28347918","tid":1361870,"uid":267189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:39:06.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0JMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=11ec0126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"}]}